name: Bogey's Indoor Golf
full_address: 3515 Fairview Industrial Dr SE, Salem, OR 97302
description: Bogey's Indoor Golf, Salem's premier golf and sports lounge experience for the whole family, opened its doors on July 13, 2024. Nestled conveniently at 3515 Fairview Industrial Drive SE, Bogey's boasts Golden Tee, BullShooter Darts, pinball and state-of-the-art golf simulators, ensuring immersive and enjoyable golf play for all skill levels. With a vibrant sports lounge atmosphere, you're guaranteed a grand time whether you're a seasoned golfer or just looking for a unique entertainment spot. Get ready for the unparalleled golfing journey that awaits you at Bogey's Indoor Golf!

name: The Sim House by NWGolfGuys
description: This Sim House is an Indoor golf facility built for golfers by golfers. Our two simulator rooms are powered by Foresight Sports GC Hawk technology and are available from 5am-midnight for members. Hourly use passes are also available. Run by NWGolfguys, the largest handicapping club and amateur tournament series in Oregon, Washington and Norcal. We also feature retail, club demos and monthly hosted tournaments. We can't wait to see you at The Sim House!

name: Middlefield Golf Course
reviews_tags: shape, price, pro shop, gentleman, area, beer, interstate, hair, rate, 2024
description: Middlefield Golf Course is a beautiful, 18-hole public course located in Cottage Grove, Oregon. The course has easy access from Interstate 5 by taking the Cottage Grove exit (exit 174). The course is a challenging 18-hole course surrounded by mature landscaping. The course is a 5002 yard par 67 course. The City of Cottage Grove purchased Middlefield Golf Course in December, 2006 and continues to operate the course. We also now offer a Golf Simulator experience. WE ARE RE-OPENING AFTER THE JANUARY 2024 ICE STORM ON FRIDAY, MARCH 29TH!
